Map: fraggit_skyfix.bsp
Version: fraggit_skyfix

Map Notes
20 Man Map.
Small basic map that should be ok for all types of counter strike source gameplay, except surf.
Designed with gungame in mind.
Exploding Car.


The previous version was tested on a public server, feedback was positive on the game play, so hopefully this new version with new fixes n features should top it.


OK this version should of fixed the bug that was sometimes occurring in fraggit.bsp, also includes the following new features (thanks to those who suggested these from my first map, fraggit.bsp)

New Textures.
New sky fix.
New lighting.
2 New hidden teleports.

**UPDATED**
Fixed teleports & lighting leak.

Any bugs, glitches, suggestions or comments are welcome as always

~cyborg
